# Review: Style Rewrite Tab — Narrative Mode

## Tổng quan

File chính: [rewrite_style_tab.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py) (3751 dòng)
Core functions: [rewriter.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py) (2774 dòng)

Narrative mode được xử lý bởi method [_do_renew_style()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#2060-2596) (L2060–2595), một pipeline 8 bước chạy tuần tự trên worker thread.

---

## Pipeline Flow Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["📂 Scan Folder / Add Files"] --> B["▶ Narrative button clicked"]
    B --> C["Niche Check (Flash AI)"]
    C --> D["_create_and_submit_job()"]
    D --> E["_do_renew_style()"]
    
    E --> S1["Step 1: Concatenate input texts"]
    S1 --> S2["Step 2: detect_framework()"]
    S2 --> S3["Step 3: extract_blueprint()"]
    S3 --> S4["Step 4: Select framework\n(AI ranking → User popup)"]
    S4 --> S5["Step 5: generate_renew_outline_v2()"]
    S5 --> S6["Step 6: audit_outline()"]
    S6 --> S7["Step 7: write_from_blueprint()\n× N chapters (sequential)"]
    S7 --> S8["Step 8: review_narrative_full()\n+ auto-patch"]
    S8 --> M["Merge → FULL_SCRIPT.txt"]
    M --> V["🎬 Cut Video (optional)"]
    V --> X["📊 Excel Update (optional)"]
    
    style S4 fill:#ffd700,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style S7 fill:#66bb6a,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style S8 fill:#ef5350,stroke:#333,color:#fff
```

---

## Chi tiết 8 bước Pipeline

### Step 1: Concatenate Text (L2163–2169)
- Gộp tất cả file `.txt` đã chọn thành 1 chuỗi `full_text`
- Format: `=== PART N: filename ===`

### Step 2: Detect Framework (L2174–2195)
- Gọi [detect_framework()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#L930-L1001) → xác định framework gốc
- Tier: dùng tier được user chọn (Pro/Flash)
- Output: `_detection.json` → `{detected_framework, confidence, reasoning}`

### Step 3: Extract Blueprint (L2197–2218)
- Gọi [extract_blueprint()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#L1004-L1044)
- Trích xuất **chỉ facts/events/themes** — không giữ original text
- Output: `_blueprint.json` → `{core_topic, key_facts, key_events, arguments, emotional_core}`

### Step 4: Select Framework (L2221–2326)
- **Manual**: User chọn từ dropdown → bỏ qua AI ranking
- **Auto**: AI rank tất cả frameworks → hiện popup cho user chọn
  - Worker thread block tại `_fw_ranking_event.wait()`
  - UI thread hiện dialog qua signal `_fw_ranking_request`
  - Output: `_rankings.json`

### Step 5: Generate Outline (L2328–2354)
- Gọi [generate_renew_outline_v2()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#L1194-L1251)
- Input: blueprint + style_json + **mandatory framework name**
- Không nhận original text → ngăn AI copy
- Output: `_renew_outline.json` → `{chapters: [{title, summary, key_points, emotional_beat, ends_with}]}`

### Step 6: Audit Outline (L2356–2383)
- Gọi [audit_outline()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#L1254-L1319)
- Kiểm tra structural issues, sửa nếu cần
- Output: `_audit.json`, `_renew_outline_audited.json` (nếu có fix)

### Step 7: Write Chapters (L2385–2483)
- Viết tuần tự từng chapter bằng [write_from_blueprint()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#L1322-L1403)
- **Sliding context N-2**: mỗi chapter nhận 2 chapter trước làm `previous_context`
- Word count rule khác nhau theo position: [open](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#554-560) (ch đầu), [body](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#598-606) (giữa), [end](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1631-1686) (ch cuối)
- Filename: `ch_01_Intro.txt`, `ch_02_Title.txt`, ...
- Title (line đầu) bị strip khi lưu file riêng, nhưng giữ nguyên trong `rewritten_texts[]`

### Step 8: Cross-chapter Review + Auto-patch (L2485–2563)
- Gọi [review_narrative_full()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py) → đánh giá flow toàn bộ
- Auto-patch: issues có severity `critical`/`major` → gọi [patch_chapter_overlap()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1535-1585)
- Dùng `rw_index_map` để map subset index → original index (tránh lệch nếu có chapter fail)
- Output: `_review.json`, `FULL_SCRIPT.txt`

---

## So sánh Narrative vs Review Pipeline

| Aspect | **Narrative** (8 steps) | **Review** (12 steps) |
|---|---|---|
| Entry point | [_do_renew_style()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#2060-2596) | [_do_renew_review()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#2642-3751) |
| Blueprint | [extract_blueprint()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1004-1045) — generic | [extract_blueprint_review()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1047-1091) — product-focused |
| Extra steps | — | Reality check, Spec verify, Price enrich, Convert units, Unused chapters copy |
| Outline fn | [generate_renew_outline_v2()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1194-1252) | [create_review_outline()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2458-2590) / [create_mystery_outline()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2321-2456) |
| Write fn | [write_from_blueprint()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1322-1404) | [write_review_chapter()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2592-2774) |
| Review fn | [review_narrative_full()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1489-1533) | [review_cross_chapter()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1148-1192) |
| Dual-framework | ❌ | ✅ (auto-dual mode) |
| Transitions | N/A | Configurable checkbox |
| Country/Units | ❌ | ✅ (US/EU conversion) |

